body:
A simple java based comic book reader.
Capable of reading .cbr, .cbz, .zip, .rar files containing image files.
Image formats supported include .jpg, .png, .gif, .bmp, .wbmp.
name: Elite Comix Reader
tagline: A simple java based comic book reader.
